elements.name: Search Function Test on Consumer Page

embeddings.name: Search Function Test on Consumer Page

steps.name: user searches for "haircut" in "San Francisco" on consumers page
verify the number of the search results are 3 or more
user selects "All services" in the services filter from the left panel
user selects second staff from the staff filter in the left side panel
user clicks the “Book” button for the “Men's Haircut” service
user presses "Select Time" in the add-on modal opened
Verify that the user is presented with a list of available time slots with at least 2 entries
verify in the right side panel :Service displayed is the one selected in the step before
verify in the right side panel :Service price is the same as the one displayed in the step before
verify in the right side panel :Staff selected is the staff chosen before
